00:26:49.053 --> 00:26:50.974
the layers of what we're learning now,

00:26:51.756 --> 00:26:53.298
so much of it becomes so vivid.

00:26:55.441 --> 00:26:57.623
But, you know,

00:26:57.702 --> 00:26:59.483
I think God's in a position, Mike,

00:26:59.923 --> 00:27:00.765
in this regard,

00:27:00.785 --> 00:27:02.306
