00:29:59.002 --> 00:30:01.564
That's our operating system.

00:30:02.005 --> 00:30:04.645
The fact that we're not afraid of really

00:30:04.846 --> 00:30:07.686
bad people.

00:30:08.166 --> 00:30:09.528
