01:33:43.306 --> 01:33:44.028
of the process.

01:33:44.387 --> 01:33:45.648
We need to make them so we can

01:33:45.689 --> 01:33:47.109
correct them and learn from them.

01:33:50.342 --> 01:33:52.283
When you realize that that's part of the

01:33:52.323 --> 01:33:54.244
process and that it's fun to learn,

01:33:54.284 --> 01:33:55.345
it's fun to grow,

01:33:55.385 --> 01:33:57.185
it's fun to find affirmations.

01:33:57.485 --> 01:33:59.006
It's really fun to stumble into something

01:33:59.027 --> 01:34:01.868
