01:34:31.844 --> 01:34:33.045
That's not how Yahweh sees us.

01:34:34.845 --> 01:34:38.506
He only sees the good, even in Kevin.

01:34:45.784 --> 01:34:48.608
You were among the first to hear this,

01:34:48.967 --> 01:34:49.307
Kevin,

01:34:49.328 --> 01:34:53.993
