02:40:58.505 --> 02:41:01.888
of Adam's life, they coexisted together.

02:41:02.689 --> 02:41:04.409
And that was a very small community back

02:41:04.469 --> 02:41:07.051
then of Nassama men.

02:41:08.212 --> 02:41:12.217
