02:41:47.263 --> 02:41:51.066
Dode, his beloved son, supporting Dode,

02:41:51.085 --> 02:41:51.825
the way it had to happen.

02:41:55.102 --> 02:41:58.224
So that's how I read this is that

02:42:01.284 --> 02:42:03.066
we didn't go back in time,

02:42:03.685 --> 02:42:05.226
but we were there at this time.

02:42:06.367 --> 02:42:08.406
And that I knew by the way this

02:42:08.447 --> 02:42:09.727
thing is introduced and the way that it

02:42:09.768 --> 02:42:15.529
concludes that the reason I could do at

02:42:15.588 --> 02:42:20.290
