02:42:20.331 --> 02:42:21.751
Yahweh could not.

02:42:21.771 --> 02:42:23.611
Yahweh couldn't talk to him directly.

02:42:25.154 --> 02:42:26.454
And Nathan couldn't get his attention.

02:42:29.175 --> 02:42:29.515
Is that,

02:42:29.575 --> 02:42:31.296
do you know if he inserted me here

02:42:31.415 --> 02:42:34.096
