02:43:02.050 --> 02:43:02.550
this work.

02:43:04.252 --> 02:43:05.391
And this is why we're going to make

02:43:05.451 --> 02:43:05.811
it work.

02:43:06.111 --> 02:43:07.051
And this is how it's going to turn

02:43:07.112 --> 02:43:09.212
