02:43:09.253 --> 02:43:15.474
That's how it happened.

02:43:15.494 --> 02:43:16.295
That's my take on it.

02:43:16.354 --> 02:43:17.354
I've been doing this a long time,

02:43:17.375 --> 02:43:18.215
a quarter of a century.

02:43:19.155 --> 02:43:21.036
And that's where God has taken my

02:43:21.056 --> 02:43:22.675
