02:43:36.831 --> 02:43:40.853
to total and complete comfort because

02:43:41.134 --> 02:43:43.396
you're now prepared to handle it and you

02:43:43.435 --> 02:43:45.756
know that you've been through it before.

02:43:47.718 --> 02:43:50.661
It worked out fine then.

02:43:50.700 --> 02:43:52.461
Young man, young man, it may be.

02:43:52.960 --> 02:43:54.662
a quarter century now, but young man,

02:43:54.701 --> 02:43:56.542
it's really fifty four hundred years, sir.

02:43:57.404 --> 02:43:57.924
Yes, it is.

02:43:58.384 --> 02:43:59.584
We've been doing this for a long time.

02:44:00.825 --> 02:44:02.006
And with each passing day,

02:44:02.086 --> 02:44:03.608
I realized more and more and more of

02:44:03.628 --> 02:44:06.590
what we have done in the past and

02:44:06.709 --> 02:44:10.211
that this is not bragging by any stretch

02:44:10.231 --> 02:44:13.693
of the imagination because it's strictly a

02:44:13.734 --> 02:44:14.254
support role.

02:44:16.556 --> 02:44:17.335
I mean,

02:44:17.377 --> 02:44:19.157
nothing but really a projection of, yeah,

02:44:19.177 --> 02:44:19.397
I was

02:44:20.450 --> 02:44:22.652
love for his son and for his people.

02:44:23.833 --> 02:44:26.674
