02:44:55.648 --> 02:44:56.190
We've never built...

02:44:58.802 --> 02:45:00.245
detoured from that in any way.

02:45:00.325 --> 02:45:03.728
It's the exact same systematic approach

02:45:04.829 --> 02:45:05.309
