So we have a different relationship,

02:45:40.543 --> 02:45:41.144
JB and I,

02:45:43.191 --> 02:45:43.871
you and I, Mike,

02:45:43.971 --> 02:45:47.058
and that you and I began by you

02:45:47.097 --> 02:45:48.180
telling me I was wrong.

02:45:48.941 --> 02:45:52.208
And JB and I began by me telling

02:45:52.289 --> 02:45:53.149
him I was wrong.

02:45:53.971 --> 02:45:54.211
And

02:45:55.764 --> 02:45:57.765
by him being an agnostic and him finding

02:45:57.806 --> 02:45:59.206
