02:46:14.531 --> 02:46:14.951
I was wrong.

02:46:14.971 --> 02:46:15.932
Let's make the correction.

02:46:16.992 --> 02:46:19.593
And being thrilled to have the opportunity

02:46:19.632 --> 02:46:20.994
to make the correction rather than

02:46:21.334 --> 02:46:21.974
bemoaning it.

02:46:22.334 --> 02:46:23.854
Every time that I learned something where

02:46:23.875 --> 02:46:24.315
I was wrong,

02:46:25.852 --> 02:46:26.174
In fact,

02:46:26.674 --> 02:46:31.518
I would say that you were the person,

02:46:31.737 --> 02:46:35.000
and I hope we can do this program

02:46:35.020 --> 02:46:35.980
