02:47:10.831 --> 02:47:11.332
prove that,

02:47:11.752 --> 02:47:14.334
but the terms that he uses for standing

02:47:14.375 --> 02:47:18.780
grain is such that it is a completely

02:47:19.139 --> 02:47:20.281
different concept

02:47:20.822 --> 02:47:21.962
than Bokurum,

02:47:22.282 --> 02:47:24.084
which is the grain is still growing,

02:47:24.144 --> 02:47:24.584
it's green,

02:47:24.644 --> 02:47:28.226
it's receptive and barley is sickled very

02:47:28.345 --> 02:47:30.727
early and they process before it's matured

02:47:30.846 --> 02:47:32.327
and it dries in the field where if

02:47:32.347 --> 02:47:34.049
