02:47:35.174 --> 02:47:37.094
And so wheat is standing grain that is

02:47:37.235 --> 02:47:38.575
ready to be harvested.

02:47:38.674 --> 02:47:39.476
And it's still,

02:47:40.915 --> 02:47:44.438
it's reached its pinnacle in terms of what

02:47:44.458 --> 02:47:45.757
it's going to be able to do.

02:47:46.619 --> 02:47:47.498
And you were saying,

02:47:47.599 --> 02:47:48.379
I was writing something.

02:47:48.398 --> 02:47:49.479
He said, no, you got that wrong.

02:47:49.540 --> 02:47:51.120
