02:47:53.101 --> 02:47:53.681
He said, by the way,

02:47:54.422 --> 02:47:56.843
you've covered this correctly in the past.

02:47:57.163 --> 02:47:58.984
You're just not recalling which you've

02:47:59.343 --> 02:48:00.183
