02:48:57.069 --> 02:48:58.770
But what you're saying right here is

02:48:59.090 --> 02:49:02.550
inconsistent with what you have written.

02:49:02.630 --> 02:49:03.570
And so I read it all.

02:49:04.091 --> 02:49:06.210
I went back and every reference to

02:49:06.412 --> 02:49:07.932
anything remotely like this,

02:49:08.352 --> 02:49:11.372
I read it from beginning to end.

02:49:11.893 --> 02:49:14.993
And it immediately said, absolutely.

02:49:15.013 --> 02:49:16.593
I was right in the middle of rewriting

02:49:16.713 --> 02:49:17.033
also

02:49:18.372 --> 02:49:20.093
questioning Paul as twistianity,

