02:51:12.372 --> 02:51:13.653
Hmm, when was that?

02:51:14.257 --> 02:51:15.539
Exact same time,

02:51:15.779 --> 02:51:18.480
exactly the same time you and I had

02:51:18.501 --> 02:51:19.522
